# 🧠 OS Concept 1: Microservices Architecture

## 1️⃣ Simple Idea

Instead of one huge application:

👉 split system into small independent services.

Each service handles one responsibility.

---

## 🧠 Real-World Analogy

Restaurant 🍽️

Instead of one person doing everything:

* one cooks
* one handles billing
* one delivers

Independent teams.

---

## ⚙️ Example

For your Women Safety App:

```text id="w8m3kp"
Auth Service
SOS Service
Location Service
Notification Service
```

Each can scale independently.

---

## Advantages

✔ scalability
✔ easier maintenance
✔ fault isolation

---

## Disadvantages

❌ more complexity
❌ network communication overhead

---

## 🎯 Placement Question

**Q: Why microservices are scalable?**

👉 Because individual services can scale independently.

---

## 🧠 Memory Trick

```text id="t4n8vz"
Microservices = many small focused services
```

