# 🧠 OS Concept 2: API Gateway

🔥 Very common backend interview topic.

---

## 1️⃣ Problem

With many microservices:

Clients should not directly contact every service.

---

## Solution

👉 API Gateway

---

## Role of API Gateway

✔ single entry point
✔ routing
✔ authentication
✔ rate limiting

---

## 🧠 Real-World Analogy

Reception desk in company 🏢

Visitors go through reception first.

---

## ⚙️ Flow

```text id="u7r2mn"
Client
  ↓
API Gateway
  ↓
Microservices
```

---

## 🎯 Placement Question

**Q: Why API gateways are useful?**

👉 They simplify client communication and centralize request handling.

---

## 🧠 Memory Trick

```text id="q5z1lx"
Gateway = traffic controller
```

